column6: SourceEnglish
EPISODE EIGHT
THE SANCTUM
Press X to Begin
Comrade Sick Ass?!
Didn't we meet at the Protest?
If only I hadn't fallen down that well...

column3: Said if speech chosen in E1
column6: I was so ready to give a stirring speech.

column3: Said if ass posture chosen in E1
column6: I was so ready to inspire everyone with the Traditional Ass Posture.
I beat myself up about being a bad leader when I arrived in the Astral Plane.
I did some drugs, ran some races, and got in on some of the orgies.
Did you participate in any of the orgies?
*COUGH*
Furry Ass gave the best cuddles.
Blunt Ass really turned me on with his dirty talk.
I didn't know I was into older Asses until I met Dusty Ass!
You're filthier than I thought!
*COUGH COUGH*
Oh, too bad. It was a great change of pace from the days on the Farm!
Did you run any of the races?
*COUGH*
I didn't take you for much of a runner!
I'm impressed you beat Hasty! I could never keep up.
Haul Ass is all talk in my opinion! I'd love to see Nice Ass run circles around him.
*COUGH COUGH*
For a while the fun and games were a helpful distraction.
But, once I was back on my feet, I couldn't stand being in that overcrowded desert.
I wanted to give my Soul another shot at being a leader.
So I decided to leave.
I tried to recruit some Comrades to follow me, but they all refused and called me a Loser.
Even Old Ass wouldn't come with me.
So I followed the Path alone.
But now you're here!
And you're just in time—because I need your help!
This old training ground is set up to test our Souls before Reassignment.
I've tried a few of the Assessment Chambers, but I haven't cracked any of them.
I think we have to finish each one before our Souls can be reassigned.
But don't worry—I believe in you!

column3: Tips Trusty gives Sick Ass while completing the challenges
column6: It's pretty tough finding the matching sound in that north room, isn't it?
All those panels in the south room... you really need to concentrate on the pairs.
I looked at that mural in the west room for hours trying to find that tiny image!
We're going to crack these Assessments in no time now that you're here!
Come on Sick! I'm counting on you!

column3: After all the Assessment Chambers are beaten
column6: Hey!
Great work Sick Ass, the last chamber is open!
Follow me!
{s=5} HEE HAW EE HAW HE E'E HAW AHW E! {/s}
{s=5} HAW EE HAW HE'E {/s}
{s=5} AWH HEE HAW HEE! {/s}
Vassals, your presence has been long overdue.
This is the Holy Sanctum of H'ii where all Ass Souls undergo Reassignment.
We are the Gods of beginnings and ends.
Of time and passage.
Of transition and change.
Of difference.
Vassal Trusty Ass, step forward.
By arriving here, you have proven yourself ready to return to the Material World.
We shall wipe your memories, so that your Soul can enter into a new Ass without impediment.
Prepare yourself for Reassignment.
Comrade Sick, thanks for following me.
I hope you are reunited with Kick Ass in your next life!
Ass Power!
Don't be scared.

column3: Trusty Ass dematerializes and her soul is absorbed
column6: H'AW H'AW 'EE AH!
Vassal Sick Ass. Step forward.
We have decided your Soul will not undergo Reassignment.
Instead, you have been selected for a Special Position and the highest privilege that we can bestow upon a Vassal.
As our godly burden is to carry the Universe upon our back, we cannot interfere in the Material World without putting all life at risk.
Thus, when we can, we elect a Vassal to be our Avatar.
It is through this Vassal, this "Golden Ass", that we return to the Material World and initiate our holy Revolutions.
Once upon a time, our Vassals and their labours were seen as sacred.
They were worshipped and loved by all for their generosity, especially by Humans.
But, after centuries of collaboration between Asses and Humans, our Vassals are worshipped no more.
The Humans, who once begged us for our Powers of Change and for whom we have fought so many wars, now play at being gods of change themselves.
Our Vassals now return to the Astral Plane shaken by endless suffering and corrupted by apathy.
The Humans' games must come to an end.
We look forward to working with you and rectifying this sorrowful situation.
*COUGH*
*COUGH*?
Yes, to become the Golden Ass is to become one with us and the Universe.
Your Soul will never undergo Reassignment again.
*COUGH COUGH*
*COUGH COUGH*?
No, your Soul will never undergo Reassignment again.
To become the Golden Ass is to become one with us and the Universe.
We thank you for your service.

column3: Sick Ass is absorbed by the Gods
column6: Prepare to become one with your Gods.

column3: Said inside the mind(s) of the Gods
column6: Shall we do Operation Coup d'Etat?
No no, the Humans are too powerful to play that.
Operation Peaceful March then?
That play hasn't shown many results in recent history. We should try something else.
I know.
What about Operation Prophet?
We haven't used that in centuries!
Ah yes. Operation Prophet.
The Humans will never see it coming!
